  "active_lock_reason": "resolved",
  "body": "This issue only happens when running on CI/CD container on linux. Works fine on macos locally.\r\n\r\nWhat I do is the following in my docker file.\r\n\r\n```js\r\nCOPY ./yarn.lock                                      /app/yarn.lock\r\nRUN yarn install --frozen-lockfile\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe error it produces is: \r\n\r\n> error An unexpected error occurred: \"https://testnet.thegraph.com/npm-registry/hardhat/-/hardhat-2.0.4.tgz: Request failed \\\"404 Not Found\\\"\".\r\n\r\nAny ideas ?\r\n\r\nI am using hardhat 2.0.4. ",
